                            <comment id="13915989" author="jukkaz" created="Fri, 28 Feb 2014 16:55:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good point about &lt;tt&gt;CopyOnWriteArrayList&lt;/tt&gt;! As you noticed, the reason for not synchronizing the read methods is to prevent writes from blocking concurrent read operations. But the reads still need to access the list of tar files that might get concurrently modified by writes, which causes this issue. Fixed in revision 1572996 by using &lt;tt&gt;CopyOnWriteArrayList&lt;/tt&gt; as suggested.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13930150" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Tue, 11 Mar 2014 09:51:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;bulk close for the 0.18 release&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
